{"tid":665101,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[第一次] 教你點用羊毛氈整公仔","createTime":"2018-05-14T15:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T09:53:03.000Z","uid":175564,"like":15,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fa666d1c151edde7fcdd39ebe576c7d3c497caa8","tid":665101,"uid":175564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:55:59.000Z","msg":"之前搞過三次日文班,好多謝參加左嘅巴絲捧場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家我地想試下d新野,睇下個反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地會教你地點用羊毛氈整下d 簡單公仔, 例如 連登emoji, 腦魔之類<br />\n難少少就可以整下tsumtsum、averger 角色公仔等。最後仲可以將佢地整成鎖匙扣添。<br />\n類似咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/14/231844_4a1fc1d505b1dfda763a48dbc281a166.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2F231844_4a1fc1d505b1dfda763a48dbc281a166.jpeg&h=76fb60ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/14/231844_ae25739dc6c345f793a9be65fca18b80.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2F231844_ae25739dc6c345f793a9be65fca18b80.jpeg&h=dd987885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/14/231845_aa8b5487121802dda1d1bab91e21aee3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2F231845_aa8b5487121802dda1d1bab91e21aee3.jpeg&h=57ecdfb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報果陣記得講下想整咩公仔,我地要預材料<br />\n費用全面,有興趣嘅巴絲可以黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n報名link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdKX0XaRsm2mxU1e4QuL6Csf3Ts6dC441SrT5cJzkTVnoGsSw/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdKX0XaRsm2mxU1e4QuL6Csf3Ts6dC441SrT5cJzkTVnoGsSw%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&